    public class FlinkMergingReduceFunction<K,AccumT,OutputT,W extends IntervalWindow>
extends FlinkReduceFunction<K,AccumT,OutputT,W>
    Special version of FlinkReduceFunction that supports merging windows. This assumes that the windows are IntervalWindows and exhibits the same behaviour as MergeOverlappingIntervalWindows.
